# 2011/08/26 jiwasaki
# Install Manual var 1.01

How to install Text::MeCab

[STEP1] let's run installer.sh
    set a env value (ROOT_DIR) :
        # e.g.
        ROOT_DIR=/home/hogehoge/myproject ./install.sh

[STEP2] running installer.sh
    configure option :
        1) choice mecab-config directory ( $INSTALL_DIR/bin/mecab-config )
        2) choice character set ( utf8 )
